definitions.definition: Any of the several muscles of the nates , each of which arises from the pelvis and inserts into a femur .
Short for gluteus maximus , either of a pair of large muscles in the human buttocks .
examples: I'm going to kick your gluteus .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) Any of the several muscles of the nates , each of which arises from the pelvis and inserts into a femur .
